description: Checklist before finishing a feature
alwaysApply: false
---

# Feature Checklist

- [ ] Business goal understood (Five Questions)
- [ ] Existing module/pattern inspected and reused
- [ ] Correct layering (action → service → repo)
- [ ] Server-side authz on every mutation
- [ ] Validation at boundary
- [ ] Tenant/org scoping
- [ ] revalidate / cache invalidation
- [ ] UX states: loading / empty / error / success
- [ ] Destructive confirmations
- [ ] No invented schema/API
- [ ] Full scope complete (when user said نفذ / كمل — not a stub)
- [ ] Self-review against Constitution
